{{!--
  semantic-depth-ladder.hbs

  Renders a stack of locution rows for a single trick (compressed →
  semantic → expanded → deep). All rows share the same font; depth is
  communicated by indentation and a depth-label chip.

  Parameters:
    ladder        — array of { depth, text } rungs (DerivationPanelEntry.ladder)
    showLabels    — optional boolean; when true renders the depth chips
                    on the left. Defaults to true.

  No interaction; no tooltips; no parser aesthetics. Plain typography.
--}}
<ol class="semantic-depth-ladder">
{{#each ladder}}
  <li class="semantic-depth-ladder-rung semantic-depth-ladder-rung--{{depth}}">
    <span class="semantic-depth-ladder-chip">{{depth}}</span>
    <span class="semantic-depth-ladder-text">{{text}}</span>
  </li>
{{/each}}
</ol>
